prompt: A small panda helping a young fox trapped under a log in an enchanted forest
revised_prompt: A miniature panda with gleaming black and white fur is seen demonstrating kindness and compassion in an enchanted woodland. The panda is assisting a juvenile fox with bright orange fur and curious eyes, who has unfortunately become trapped beneath a fallen tree log. The woodland around them is bathed in a magical glow, adding an element of wonder and fantasy to the scene. Mossy tree trunks, colorful wildflowers, and vibrant mushrooms add to the mystical allure. A soft luminescence radiates from the leaves above, casting a dappled light on this touching encounter.
